import { Box, Card, CardBody, CardHeader, Center } from "@chakra-ui/react";

export default function Song() {
    return (
        <Box position="relative" marginX={30} >
            <Card w="50vw" h="20vh" borderRadius="35px" minHeight="90px">
                <CardBody >
                    <CardHeader>
                        <Box>
                            <Image
                                borderRadius='full'
                                boxSize='150px'
                                src='https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gatopedia/images/2/2f/Bingus.png/revision/latest/thumbnail/width/360/height/360?cb=20230104171932&path-prefix=es'
                                alt='Dan Abramov'
                            />
                        </Box>
                    </CardHeader>
                </CardBody>
            </Card>
        </Box>
    );
}
